message:
PR #34965: Bump actions/checkout from 6.0.0 to 6.0.1 Imported from GitHub PR https://github.com/openxla/xla/pull/34965 Bumps [actions/checkout](https://github.com/actions/checkout) from 6.0.0 to 6.0.1.
Release notes

Sourced from actions/checkout's releases.

v6.0.1

What's Changed

  • Update all references from v5 and v4 to v6 by @​ericsciple in actions/checkout#2314
  • Add worktree support for persist-credentials includeIf by @​ericsciple in actions/checkout#2327
  • Clarify v6 README by @​ericsciple in actions/checkout#2328

Full Changelog: https://github.com/actions/checkout/compare/v6...v6.0.1
